comments.text: From what I heard, the contraversy of Subnautica 2 is very up in the air. The creators claim they weren't allowed to put the game up to early access when they wanted missing their deadline for players to get a mega bonus for the studio. Honestly it's hard to tell who's taking advantage of who as both have something to gain from this.
